      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your exhaustion is valid, and the feeling that your efforts are futile against such vast destruction is a heavy burden to carry. It is okay to step back from the pressure to be a hero or to fix everything alone; sometimes, the only way to survive the burn is to stop trying to put it out. You don't have to find meaning in the collapse; you can simply choose to exist without the weight of the world on your shoulders.",
      "source": "target",
